\[h = \sqrt{5^2 - 4^2} = 3.\]Hence,
\begin{align*}
[\triangle PAB] &= \frac{1}{2} \cdot 6 \cdot 4 = 12, \\
[\triangle PBC] &= \frac{1}{2} \cdot 6 \cdot 4 = 12, \\
